data.description: Here is you chance to live in desirable and rarely available Cypress Club in the Highlands Community.    Contemporary design with open stair case and loft area with 20 foot ceiling makes it airy and open. This townhome is situated near the community's private pool. Step outside the screen patio enjoy a cozy sitting area for a bbq. Unit includes 2 designated parking spots directly in front. Also included is a personal storage space.  The master community offers miles of walking, a nature trail tennis. volleyball & basketball courts.  Ideally located in Winter Springs
